{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1707-10C_65","head":{"value":"Canson su la retreto dau Duc de Savoyo. Su l’Air : De Madamo la Duchesso","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Histoire du siège de Toulon, seconde partie","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", [Mercure galant], octobre 1707 [tome 12], p. 65-78.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":["Comme suivant l’usage ordinaire du monde, les uns pleurent dans le temps que les autres rient, plusieurs pleuroient la perte de leurs parens ou de leurs amis tuez depuis l’entrée de Monsieur le Duc de Savoye en Provence, jusqu’au jour de son retour dans ses Etats, d’autres estoient occupez à chanter les Chansons suivantes, ou à se divertir à la lecture des autres Vers qui les accompagnent.","Les deux premieres Chansons sont en langage Provençal, &amp; quoy que la troisiéme ne soit pas dans le même langage, il paroist neanmoins qu’elle a esté faite par un Provençal, qui croyant parler ce langage, n’a pas observé exactement toutes les regles de la Poësie : mais il est certain que l’on trouve beaucoup d’esprit dans cette Chanson."],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"CANSON SU LA RETRETO DAU DUC DE SAVOYO.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Su l’Air : ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De Madamo la Duchesso","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/hi/#"}},"#3":{"value":".","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#3"}}},{"lg":{"l":["Pus qu’en grando rejoüissenço,","Tous leis Troubadours de Provenço,","S’exerçon en milo façouns,","Per fay clata noüestro joyo,","Celebren per qu’auqueis Cansouns,","Leis exploits dau Duc de Savoyo."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Ven eme uno puissanto Armado,","Groussido per la Renoumado,","Nous trobo senso deffensours,","D’aqui councebet l’esperanço,","D’estre en état din pau de jours,","D’englouti l’Espagno &amp; la Franço."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Despuis long-temps la grand Bretaigno,","La Houlando, ny l’Allemagno,","N’avien insulta noüestreis Borts,","Jamay su Mar, jamay su Terro,","N’avian sustengut leis efforts,","D’uno plus dangeirouso Guerro."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Passo lou Var eme insoulenço,","Et crés d’abort que la Prouvenço,","Vendra se soumettre à sa Ley,","May rescontro un Pople fidele,","Qu’és penetrat per son grand Rey,","De respect, d’amour &amp; de zele."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" À l’houro rampli de coulero,","Creignen lou sort de son grand pero,","Parlo ensin à seis Camisars,","Messiers m’avias tous fa proumesso,","D’unir souto meis Estandars,","Tous leis enemis de la Messo."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Per apeisar aquel ouragi,","Seignour non perdés pas couragi,","L’y dis un de seis Predicans,","N’avés qu’à passa la Durenço,","Serés joung per ley Proutestans,","De Languedoc, &amp; de Prouvenço."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Serié lou veritable affayre,","Seriou Mestre senso ista gayre,","Et dau Coumtat &amp; d’Avignon,","May aquo noun s’y pau pas fayre ;","Car la Reyno Anno vou Toulon,","Per son argent l’y fau coumplayre."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Se mette d’abort en Campagno,","Per tout la terrour l’accoumpagno,","Lou vol &amp; lou saccajament,","L’assassinat, lou brigandagi,","La troumparié, lou brulamen,","Soun leis fourriers de soun passagi."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Per tout la paraulo es manquado,","La fé per tout es vioulado,","Témoin lou Noble Merindou,","Que per un accident sinistre,","Dins lou tems que n’avié plus poou,","Perdet doux escus &amp; soun ristre."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Ven à Toulon, &amp; son Armado,","Coumenço per son arribado,","De fayre juga lou Canon,","Lors que la Villo encourageado,","Respoüende su lou même ton,","Canounado per Canounado."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Prince d’équivoque merite,","Arrestas vous, anas trop vite,","Vous aprendren en aquest jour,","Per voüestro vergougnouso fuito,","Que ço que vous ven dau Tambour,","Sentourno souvent per la Fluito."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#1":{"value":" Arrestas-vous ","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Tessé","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" s’avanço,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#2"}},"Coundus leis Bataillons de Franço,","Que joungs eme noüestreis Marins,","Ajustaran à voüestre eloge,","Un d’aquesteis quatre matins,",{"#1":{"value":"Lou surnom de ","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[5]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jâque Déloge","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[5]/#2"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#1":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Medavy","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" déja vous resserro,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#2"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Grignan","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" vous fa manqua de Terro,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Guebriant","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" vous coüigno de prés,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/#"}},"Que fan changea su voüestro testo,","Tous voüestreis Lauriés en Ciprés,","Ben que n’aguessias pas de resto."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[26]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Quittas un dessein temerari,","Prenes un conseou salutari,","Se non poudés prendre Toulon,","Dirés eis Princes de la Liguo,","Qu’avés coupa qu’auque Melon,","Mangea lou Rasin &amp; la Figuo."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[28]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Per qu’auqueis Maisons abimados,","Per qu’auqueis Vignos derrabados,","Per qu’auque Vilagi roüinat,","Tiras pas un grand avantagi,","Sias vengut, vous sias entournat,","Que poudias fayre d’avantagi."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[30]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Partés n’avés ren à pretendre,","N’esperés pas que voüestre Gendre ;","Per augmenta voüestre chagrin,","Seguit de la valour Franceso,","Non se revenge sus Turin,","De voüestro ourgueüillouso entrepreso."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[32]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[" Au soulet brut de sa vendugo,","S’avés juga à l’escoundudo,","Avés agi foüer sageament :","Et per aquo din la Prouvenço,","Cantaren eternelament,","À l’hounour de voüestro prudenço."]}},{"p":{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chasteüil Galaup.","id":"/div/quote/#[34]/p/hi/#"}}}}]}}}